   - Any other email or anti-spam laws applicable in your jurisdiction.

3. SMTP PROVIDER TERMS OF SERVICE
   You are responsible for complying with the terms of service of any SMTP
   relay provider used with this software (e.g. Brevo, SendGrid, AWS SES).
   The author accepts no liability for account suspension or termination
