4. NO SPAM OR MALICIOUS USE
   This software must not be used to send unsolicited bulk email (spam),
   phishing messages, malware, or any content that is illegal, deceptive,
   or harmful. It is designed exclusively for warming up owned domains to
   improve legitimate email deliverability.

5. NO WARRANTY
   The author makes no guarantees regarding email deliverability outcomes,
   inbox placement rates, or domain reputation improvements. Results depend
